{"tid":1116933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【邊個賣獎？】十大中文金曲獎座被拍賣 港台回應︰感到詫異、失望同可惜","createTime":"2019-04-20T10:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T03:03:18.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"90f93def35a136d06b8a9f5cf6a4d4bc6c7efe29","tid":1116933,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"不論歌影視界，獎座對藝人來說，是一種肯定和鼓勵，不過獎座被掉棄及變賣的事，屢有發生。今日《蘋果》讀者司徒小姐，在一個拍賣網站中發現，有人以標題「十大中文金曲獎座 老香港懷舊物品」，將一個「十大中文金曲」的獎座進行拍賣，底價為1,000元。<br />\n讀者司徒小姐表示，她在拍賣網中發現有人賣獎，她說︰「剛才我喺網上見到，詳情我唔太清楚，我只覺得如果呢個獎係頒過畀嗰位得獎人，又或者呢個獎係sample都好，都唔應該攞出嚟咁樣賣。」據她提供的拍賣網頁中，可見到放賣的人，於2個月前放上網頁兜售，至今沒有人還價，亦未能成功賣出。而該拍賣帖附上的6張相中，其中4張相清楚可見是港台頒發的「十大中文金曲」的獎座，但獎座下方遮了得獎人名字，另外兩張相，分別是葉蒨文和容祖兒分別於2011年及2017年得獎時捧住獎拍的相片。<br />\n對於網上有人拍賣十大中文金曲獎座，港台公關部發言人今日回覆《蘋果》表示︰「金曲獎座每一年頒出，係表揚對中文流行樂壇幕前幕後有貢獻嘅傑出人士，表揚佢哋嗰一年嘅成就、成績，港台送出嘅獎座由得獎人保留，對於有人出售，港台感到詫異、失望同可惜。」<br />\n其實今年2月發生掉獎事件，當時商台DJ Colin Mak路經北角渣華道橋底，發現一個於2013年新城勁爆頒獎禮中，頒發的「新城勁爆躍進歌手」獎座，如垃圾被拋在橋底。網民更鎖定五位歌手為「可疑人物」，如連詩雅、羅力威、龍小菌、蔚雨芯及吳彤。（相關新聞︰ <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2BsD5XQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2BsD5XQ&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=92a29bf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2BsD5XQ</a> ）<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190420/large/1555750882_7228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190420%2Flarge%2F1555750882_7228.jpg&h=60247521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190420/59510745\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190420%2F59510745&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=e2420708\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190420%2F59510745&h=5e0c6e4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190420/59510745</a>"},{"pid":"84f6da95eec9377f06af176215ff16e380487d6e","tid":1116933,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.carousell.com/p/212615572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.carousell.com%2Fp%2F212615572&d=v6UOKjiqNHu3M1gE0B2GLKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=68b8e3a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.carousell.com/p/212615572</a>"},{"pid":"638d5c11ad51c234b712c783f4f580eec3a037b0","tid":1116933,"uid":71493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:53:03.000Z","msg":"又係佢幾個"},{"pid":"e959e3a2e673cca400117654d188deb7ec7fcfe8","tid":1116933,"uid":3962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:54:31.000Z","msg":"又唔係叱咤or九十年代勁歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾獎"},{"pid":"9963a17ba829ff8444d6b4976d270f122a2d6343","tid":1116933,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T16:33:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為梅姐遺物又比人賣"},{"pid":"fa3328183dbd796d66a4b95fd466838f7df834be","tid":1116933,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e959e3a2e673cca400117654d188deb7ec7fcfe8","tid":1116933,"uid":3962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:54:31.000Z","msg":"又唔係叱咤or九十年代勁歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾獎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3352196e6865070bcf43279c0a1bac09b7e3381f","tid":1116933,"uid":146720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T02:45:09.000Z","msg":"想要<